                           </q>
                           <note>The note was written in Italian in the <date>mid-16th century</date>. It states that 
                              <persName ref="PRS11376Fioravanti">Leonardo Fioravanti</persName> was living  near Castel Nuovo in Naples, and that he healed the 
                              one who wrote the note, a certain <persName ref="PRS11377Matera">Giovanni Jacobo Matera</persName>.</note>
                        </item>
                        
